text: John Rolfe (1585–1622) was an English settler of Virginia and husband of Pocahontas. John Rolfe may also refer to: *John Carew Rolfe (1859–1943), American classicist *John Rolfe (actor), British actor *John Rolph (politician) (1793–1870), Canadian lawyer and politician ==See also== *John Rolph (disambiguation)
title: John Rolfe (disambiguation)
